}}'''新未來城'''（{{Lang-ar|نيوم}}，Neom）是[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]西北部[[塔布克省|塔布克省]]的一个规划中的跨境城市。它被規劃為[[智慧城市|智慧城市]]和旅遊城市。该地靠近[[红海|红海]]、[[蒂朗海峽|蒂朗海峽]]以及[[埃及|埃及]]、[[以色列|以色列]]和约旦的边界<ref>[https://www.skynewsarabia.com/web/article/990920/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B3%D8%B9%D9%88%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%AA%D8%B7%D9%84%D9%82-%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9-%D9%86%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%85-%D8%A8%D8%AF%D8%B9%D9%85-%D9%8A%D8%AA%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B2-500-%D9%85%D9%84%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%AF%D9%88%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B1 "نيوم".. تفاصيل أضخم مشروع سعودي ممتد بين 3 دول] سكاي نيوز عربية, نشر في 24 أكتوبر 2017 ودخل في 24 أكتوبر 2017.</ref>。它的总面积为26500平方公里，並沿着红海海岸延伸460公里。

沙特阿拉伯當局目标是在2025年之前先建成新未來城的一期項目<ref>{{Cite web|title=Saudi Arabia to Begin Building Homes in $500 Billion Futuristic City Neom|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-01-16/saudi-arabia-to-begin-building-homes-in-futuristic-city-neom|accessdate=2020-03-10|date=2019-01-16|work=Bloomberg.com|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204023511/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-01-16/saudi-arabia-to-begin-building-homes-in-futuristic-city-neom|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Everything we know about Neom, a 'mega-city' project in Saudi Arabia with plans for flying cars and robot dinosaurs|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/neom-what-we-know-saudi-arabia-500bn-mega-city-2019-9|accessdate=2020-03-10|author=Bostock|first=Bill|work=Business Insider|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325052253/https://www.businessinsider.com/neom-what-we-know-saudi-arabia-500bn-mega-city-2019-9|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该项目建設成本估计为5000亿美元。2019年1月29日，沙特阿拉伯宣布注資5000亿美元成立一家名为NEOM的封闭式股份公司<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/saudi-neom-idUKL5N1ZT4C9|title=UPDATE 1-Saudi NEOM set up as joint stock company run by state fund...|date=2019-01-29|work=Reuters|accessdate=2019-01-29|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029115114/https://uk.reuters.com/article/saudi-neom-idUKL5N1ZT4C9|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这家由沙特的[[主权财富基金|主权财富基金]][[沙烏地阿拉伯公共投資基金|沙烏地阿拉伯公共投資基金]]全资拥有的公司負責开发新未來城的经济開發区<ref>{{Cite web|title=Saudi Arabia announces creation of Neom Company|url=http://www.arabnews.com/node/1443891/saudi-arabia|accessdate=2019-01-29|date=2019-01-29|work=Arab News|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225113815/https://www.arabnews.com/node/1443891/saudi-arabia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新未來城计划完全由[[可再生能源|可再生能源]]供电<ref>{{Cite web|title=Submerged floating bridge wins 'Dream NEOM' contest in KSA|url=http://www.arabnews.com/node/1482091/saudi-arabia|accessdate=2019-04-14|date=2019-04-13|work=Arab News|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413212950/http://www.arabnews.com/node/1482091/saudi-arabia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

